Baisc Info¶

模型分为三个部分，generator, upsampler_256, upsampler_1024, 三者的training beta schedule不一样如下：

{
    "generator_config": {
        "schedule": "cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "learned_range"
    },
    "upsampler_256_config": {
        "schedule": "cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    },
    "upsampler_1024_config": {
        "schedule": "linear",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    }
}

原模型ddim生成结果是这样的：

In [2]:
res = p({"text": "一个苹果", "order": 2, "method": "multistep"})

plt.imshow(res['output_img'])

尝试把generator的ddim改成dpm

In [3]:
diffusion_params = {
    "generator_config": {
        "schedule": "discrete:cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "learned_range",
        "use_dpm": True
    },
    "upsampler_256_config": {
        "schedule": "cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    },
    "upsampler_1024_config": {
        "schedule": "linear",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    }
}
p.model.update_diffusion_params(diffusion_params)

出来的就是如上这种图片，尝试过不同的setting（order，method等），结果差别不大。 下面尝试替换upsampler_1024的ddim为dpm，即beta schedule为linear的module。

In [5]:
diffusion_params = {
    "generator_config": {
        "schedule": "cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "learned_range",
    },
    "upsampler_256_config": {
        "schedule": "cosine",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    },
    "upsampler_1024_config": {
        "schedule": "discrete:linear",
        "num_timesteps": 1000,
        "use_dpm": True,
        "var_type": "fixed_small"
    }
}
p.model.update_diffusion_params(diffusion_params)
In [6]:
res = p({"text": "一个苹果", "order": 2, "method": "multistep", "upsampler_1024_timesteps": 40})
